original_title: ROH: Bitter Friends, Stiffer Enemies II
overview: Bitter Friends, Stiffer Enemies 2 was a professional wrestling event produced by Ring of Honor (ROH). It took place on April 24, 2010 at the Frontier Fieldhouse in Chicago Ridge, Illinois. Colt Cabana & El Generico face Kevin Steen & Steve Corino in a Chicago Street Fight and more!
title: ROH: Bitter Friends, Stiffer Enemies II
